These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-4-1::.
City: berlin, venice
1. the person traveling to berlin is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |
| City   | venice | berlin |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-4-2::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, blend
1. the blend-smoker is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2     |
| Cigar   | old-henry | blend |

 #################################

 
